OL,3,CSpanish woman dies by euthanasia after
OL,4,Clong legal battle with father
OL,6,FWarning: This article contains
OL,7,Freferences to sexual assault and
OL,8,Fsuicide
OL,10,FA Spanish woman who fought a lengthy
OL,11,Flegal battle against her family for
OL,12,Fher right to end her life died by
OL,13,Feuthanasia on Thursday.
OL,15,FNoelia Castillo received life-ending
OL,16,Fmedicine in Barcelona after Spain's
OL,17,Fhigh court denied her family's appeal.
OL,18,FShe was 25.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
