OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1774598699
OL,3,CSpanish woman dies by euthanasia after
OL,4,Clong legal battle with father
OL,6,FFor over a year, Castillo pursued her
OL,7,Fright to die after her father put up a
OL,8,Flengthy legal battle after a medical
OL,9,Fbody in Catalonia approved his
OL,10,Fdaughter's request for euthanasia in
OL,11,F2024, finding her suffering severe and
OL,12,Fincurable.
OL,14,FThe public battle over Castillo's
OL,15,Fright to die came to embody the depth
OL,16,Fof feeling and division across Spain
OL,17,Fon the right to assisted dying.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1774598699
OL,3,CSpanish woman dies by euthanasia after
OL,4,Clong legal battle with father
OL,6,F"The happiness of a father or a mother
OL,7,Fshould not precede the happiness of a
OL,8,Fdaughter," Castillo told Spanish
OL,9,Fbroadcaster Antena 3 in an interview
OL,10,Faired on Wednesday, a day before her
OL,11,Fdeath.
OL,13,F"At last I've managed it, so let's see
OL,14,Fif I can finally rest now," she said,
OL,15,F"I just cannot go on anymore."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31104
