PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1774598699
OL,3,CSpanish woman dies by euthanasia after
OL,4,Clong legal battle with father
OL,6,FCastillo's parents opposed her
OL,7,Fdecision until the end, and were
OL,8,Frepresented by the conservative
OL,9,FCatholic organisation Abogados
OL,10,FCristianos in their fight to stop
OL,11,Ftheir daughter's euthanasia.
OL,13,FBut in an interview on Wednesday,
OL,14,FCastillo explained that her decision
OL,15,Fwas rooted in intense physical and
OL,16,Fmental suffering that began following
OL,17,Fa turbulent childhood.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
