CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1774598699
OL,3,CSpanish woman dies by euthanasia after
OL,4,Clong legal battle with father
OL,6,FAs a teenager, she spent time in a
OL,7,Fsupervised care centre and was
OL,8,Fdiagnosed with Obsessive-Compulsive
OL,9,FDisorder and Borderline Personality
OL,10,FDisorder.
OL,12,FShe also recounted to her interviewer
OL,13,Ftwo incidents of sexual abuse. Days
OL,14,Fafter the second incident in October
OL,15,F2022, which involved three men, she
OL,16,Fattempted suicide.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1774598699
OL,3,CSpanish woman dies by euthanasia after
OL,4,Clong legal battle with father
OL,6,FAlthough she survived her suicide
OL,7,Fattempt, she was left paraplegic and
OL,8,Fwheelchair-bound, and suffered almost
OL,9,Fconstant pain. This became the turning
OL,10,Fpoint that led her to consider
OL,11,Feuthanasia.
OL,13,F"Sleeping is very difficult for me,
OL,14,Fand besides that, I have back and leg
OL,15,Fpain," she said, but added that even
OL,16,Fbefore her physical suffering, "my
OL,17,Fworld was very dark... I had no goals,
OL,18,Fno objectives, nothing".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
