OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1774598699
OL,3,CSpanish woman dies by euthanasia after
OL,4,Clong legal battle with father
OL,6,FSpain is among nine EU countries with
OL,7,Flaws that allow people experiencing
OL,8,Funbearable suffering to access
OL,9,Fassisted dying, according to Dignity
OL,10,Fin Dying, a UK-based rights group that
OL,11,Fadvocates in favour of medically
OL,12,Fassisted suicide.
OL,14,FSince Spain adopted its euthanasia law
OL,15,Fin 2021, 1,123 people have been
OL,16,Fadministered life-ending medicine up
OL,17,Funtil the end of 2024, according to
OL,18,Fthe country's health ministry.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
