PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1774598699
OL,3,CSpanish woman dies by euthanasia after
OL,4,Clong legal battle with father
OL,6,FCastillo's request to end her life was
OL,7,Foriginally approved in July 2024 by
OL,8,Fthe Catalonia Guarantee and Evaluation
OL,9,FCommission. The commission found that
OL,10,Fshe met all legal requirements, as she
OL,11,Fhad a "nonrecoverable clinical
OL,12,Fsituation" causing "severe dependence,
OL,13,Fpain, and chronic, disabling
OL,14,Fsuffering."
OL,16,FBut in August of the same year, her
OL,17,Ffather began a legal fight to stop the
OL,18,Fprocess, arguing that she was
OL,19,Fincapable of making such a decision.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1774598699
OL,3,CSpanish woman dies by euthanasia after
OL,4,Clong legal battle with father
OL,6,F"He has not respected my decision and
OL,7,Fhe never will," Castillo said about
OL,8,Fher father.
OL,10,FHer father initiated a legal process
OL,11,Fthat delayed his daughter's euthanasia
OL,12,Ffor 20 months, going through both the
OL,13,FSpanish Supreme Court and the European
OL,14,FCourt of Human Rights.
OL,16,FBut none of these bodies opposed
OL,17,FCastillo's decision. All found she met
OL,18,Fthe requirements and was capable of
OL,19,Fdeciding to die.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1774598699
OL,3,CSpanish woman dies by euthanasia after
OL,4,Clong legal battle with father
OL,6,FSpeaking to Spanish media on
OL,7,FWednesday, Castillo said she did not
OL,8,Fwant her family to be there when she
OL,9,Fdied, claiming she was misunderstood.
OL,10,FShe also acknowledged the media
OL,11,Fspotlight her case had drawn.
OL,13,F"None of my family is in favour of
OL,14,Feuthanasia, obviously, because I'm
OL,15,Fanother pillar of the family,"
OL,16,FCastillo said, "but what about the
OL,17,Fpain that I've suffered all these
OL,18,Fyears?"
OL,20,FWho to contact if you or someone you
OL,21,Fknow needs help
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
